OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening with some
OL,7,Fpatchy light rain and the chance of
OL,8,Fsome haar. This clearing northeast
OL,9,Flate in the night to become dry with
OL,10,Fsome brightness by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry start with some
OL,13,Fbrightness. Then outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fspread east, becoming heavy for a time
OL,15,Fin the afternoon before clearing
OL,16,Fduring evening. Breezy for a time in
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
